  "detailed_description": "What Lies Between is a 3d platformer focused on speed through mastery of the simple yet <br />\r\npowerful mechanics given. Expanding your potential as you play, gaining new information <br />\r\nand abilities to more effectively navigate the open ended levels. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nGive chase to the mysterious creature that brought you to a new reality. Travel through <br />\r\ncities of endless, towering pillars. Forests shrouded in fog. Caverns overrun with shadow.<br />\r\nSnowy peaks above the world. Lands forgotten to time. <br />\r\nEven the very space between reality itself. All in the effort of returning home.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor normal gameplay, Xbox controllers will function. <br />\r\nAs of now, menus will need to be navigated using a mouse.",
